    <item>
      <title>提高反弹shell交互性</title>
      <link>https://test692618.github.io/post/%E6%B8%97%E9%80%8F%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7/%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E5%8F%8D%E5%BC%B9shell%E4%BA%A4%E4%BA%92%E6%80%A7/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 17:54:19 &#43;0000</pubDate>
      <author>knock_s@foxmial.com (L)</author>
      <guid>https://test692618.github.io/post/%E6%B8%97%E9%80%8F%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7/%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E5%8F%8D%E5%BC%B9shell%E4%BA%A4%E4%BA%92%E6%80%A7/</guid>
      <description>
        <![CDATA[<h1>提高反弹shell交互性</h1><p>作者：L（knock_s@foxmial.com）</p>
        
          <h3 id="使用python提升shell交互">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e4%bd%bf%e7%94%a8python%e6%8f%90%e5%8d%87shell%e4%ba%a4%e4%ba%92"></a>
使用python提升shell交互
</h3><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell"><span class="line"><span class="cl">Python -c <span class="s1">&#39;import pty;pty.spawn(&#34;/bin/bash&#34;)&#39;</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id="重新输出shell">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e9%87%8d%e6%96%b0%e8%be%93%e5%87%bashell"></a>
重新输出shell
</h3><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell"><span class="line"><span class="cl">获得初始shell ctrl+z 挂在后台
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">然后输入 stty raw -echo<span class="p">;</span><span class="nb">fg</span>   
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">## 这样再按ctrl+c时shell不会中断</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id="添加环境变量">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e6%b7%bb%e5%8a%a0%e7%8e%af%e5%a2%83%e5%8f%98%e9%87%8f"></a>
添加环境变量
</h3><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nb">export</span> <span class="nv">TERM</span><span class="o">=</span>xterm-color
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">## 可支持更多命令</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id="使用rlwrap进行监听">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e4%bd%bf%e7%94%a8rlwrap%e8%bf%9b%e8%a1%8c%e7%9b%91%e5%90%ac"></a>
使用rlwrap进行监听
</h3><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell"><span class="line"><span class="cl">rlwrap nc -lvvp <span class="m">666</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">## 可识别上下左右</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div>
        
        <hr><p>本文2024-01-28首发于<a href='https://test692618.github.io/'>HELLO WORLD</a>，最后修改于2024-01-28</p>]]>
      </description>
      
        <category>渗透技巧</category>
      
    </item>
    
    

    <item>
      <title>其他技巧</title>
      <link>https://test692618.github.io/post/%E6%B8%97%E9%80%8F%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7/</link>
